<h1 className={"openapi__heading"}>Import keys</h1>

<MethodEndpoint method={"post"} path={"/v2/projects/{projectId}/keys/import"}></MethodEndpoint>



Imports new keys with translations. If key already exists, its translations and tags are not updated.
